<br>
There is the Ogre in the evil section of PoK and there is a Barbarian who claims to be a past leader of the Steel Warriors in the good section of PoK.<br>
<br>
If you have a tracker available both are within Druid tracking range from the PoK/Nexus zonestone (maxed at 125 on mine).<br>
<br>
I haven't tried talking to them yet with my Planar Travel Manual equiped. <p>Scartle SoulKlaw&lt;br&gt;<br>
