<br>
Anyone have any ideas as to what this &quot;planar combat&quot; skill is? <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.cableone.net/jamez/glsigs/tal-epic.jpg"alt="Tal"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->Taliaferro Erucolindo<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->Fier'Dal Champion of Emerald and Steel<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->Wielder of the Jagged Blade of War<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->Guardian of the Shining Star of Light<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->Officer of Giliath Lang</p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorfrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=626.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorfrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=626.topic&start=41&stop=49>3</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorfrm6.showPrevMessage?topicID=626.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorfrm6.showNextMessage?topicID=626.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorfrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=626.topic&index=20><img src=http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/swaddreply.GIF border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorfrm6.emailToFriend?topicID=626.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorfrm6.threadControl?topicID=626.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ft